txt.en: The scout gives you a missive to defeat wargs or drakes.\n\n<rgb=#FF0000>Warning: This quest requires Clovengap: Terror in the Trees to be underway. If that quest has been completed or failed, you will be unable to exit and re-enter this instance in order to complete this quest.</rgb>
